title: Amid Escalating Violence, Iraqis Head To Ballot Boxes
teaser: Iraqis vote Wednesday in the country's first national election since U.S. forces withdrew in 2011. Steve Inskeep talks to Prashant Rao, Iraq bureau chief for Agence France Presse.
